# Cursor ignore patterns
# Files and folders that Cursor should ignore for context/scanning

# Archived documentation
docs/archive/**
**/*_FIX*.md
**/*COMPLETE*.md
**/*PROGRESS*.md
**/*IMPLEMENT*.md
**/*RUNBOOK*.md
**/*GUIDE*.md
**/*TODO*.md
**/*NOTES*.md

# Build and cache directories
node_modules/**
dist/**
build/**
coverage/**
.next/**
.cache/**
.tmp/**
*.log
*.log.*

# Test artifacts
coverage/**
.nyc_output/**
test-results/**
playwright-report/**

# Environment and config
.env.local
.env.*.local
*.local

# IDE and editor
.vscode/**
.idea/**
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# Git
.git/**

# Documentation that's not actively used
**/docs/archive/**

**/*DAY_*.md
